Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主人公克服了恋爱的重重阻力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终找到真命天子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱真是美妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像设定和情节都有点脱离现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归根到底只是漫画而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 什么 什么嘛 阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画和现实的区别我还是明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏又不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想委婉表达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟阿土来场那样的恋爱而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能委婉过头了他没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真 太天真了 杏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明白梦幻一般的恋爱情节在现实中是不会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还是会从心底去渴望 这就是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是如此凄惨的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有朝一日天上会掉下来一个可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是如此老土的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有朝一日会有帅哥捡到自己写的诗集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过杏可不老土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是土田老师也应该会做这样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏应该做的就是去回应他的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他来一场梦幻般的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦幻般的恋爱 梦幻般的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去邀请阿土来一场绝妙的约会就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如…碰头的时候要这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸约会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天杏要招待阿土去参加一场绝妙的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1点在院子里的长椅上等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 路上有点拥挤…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田先生 等很久了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我也才刚刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是个好天气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那身衣服是谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小chi老师借给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一说是要约会用的 她就说请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川代老师吗 那个人又耍什么宝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有一家很不错的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田先生 请问咖啡的砂糖要几块
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不用勉强学大人讲话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏也觉得有点勉强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家蛋糕店的提拉米苏很美味的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的环境也很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是露天咖啡店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田 在约会？挺厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别让女孩子请客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边玩去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的女朋友真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们俩如此般配
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是免费赠送你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免费赠送？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么说呢 阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是热带饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这是午饭喝剩下的牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇 吸管有两根 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 既然是特意准备的 那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 因为太渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是 阿土他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是约会 应该两个人一起喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为土田老师太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为土田老师还没适应和别人约会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没适应…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢杏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是回答得不谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又会哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然喜欢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是老师对学生的那种喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢 小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来我们就去兜风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜风？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我说了不该说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土 再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏看上去真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和土田老师一起出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在和阿土约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！（倍受打击）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真般配啊 小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛衣很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳快要下山了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 坐这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的公园一到晚上 气氛就好得不得了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是星空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再来一个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过5分钟下午的自由活动就结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是流星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光 闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光 闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是设计新颖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能在游戏中运用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说对着流星许愿就能成真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能跟阿土永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 你的愿望会成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光 闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 阿土也许个愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\an8}老师的愿望是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿世间的人们都能幸福地生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那种啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能早点用DS玩DQ7…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没情调
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说过吗 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个公园里有一个传说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在你们现在坐着的长椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲亲过的情侣就能永远在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝倒是很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会弄哭她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由活动时间结束 请大家回教室去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友们 结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来就准备回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后是明天的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏今晚不想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点准备回家的话 妈妈就快来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般这种时候都是拿出酒店房间的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者招待我去高级酒吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这设定还真是夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天因为杏的努力 很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊扮的是小鸡 小梅扮的是兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏不玩扮小动物的游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩昨天的后续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后续啦 后续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的后续 约会的后续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也在和土田老师约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 动物园约会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 不是啦 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯哼 因为老师要去参加亲戚的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以明天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天土田老师不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏也要和阿土举办婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 明天不要给山本老师添麻烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一天要请山本老师来照料樱班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 明天要尽量帮助山本老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和山本老师一起度过一整天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了 杏和山本老师恋爱的正面对决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花丸帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推荐这本图画书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那下回去买一本来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜 听说你今天要连樱班一起照料？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗 需要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 如果有需要我会拜托你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在两个班之间来回跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气这么好 如果没问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想用木桌在外面上课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用木桌吗？好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想昨天樱班的小朋友已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天土田老师休息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天樱班和桃班的小朋友一起上课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在这个特别的教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度过愉快的一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖暖的真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里还能看到天空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天太阳公公陪着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就由杏来代替土田老师给山本老师帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏来？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 土田老师对山本老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为阿土说了要帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就必须要好好帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏真是积极啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意料的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请多多给杏分配任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就拜托小杏给老师帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏该做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家一起来折纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏跟老师一起去桃班的教室里取一下彩色纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己一个人就能取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 彩色纸 彩色纸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 老师去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在担心小杏能不能找到放彩色纸的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 杏已经找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托小杏发给大家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人3张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这个怎么折啊 完全不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都折好郁金香了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏也折好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢老师给我倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏也要帮忙倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在院子里吃饭就像在郊游一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏还要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给杏分配工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这次就在院子里玩躲避球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避球？好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么能去道具室帮忙拿一下球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…躲避球 躲避球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 赶快 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把躲避球拿来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 抱歉哦 老师比赛中途要离开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就回来 能帮老师看着大家一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 老师要去厕所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给杏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小朋友们明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作还真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏今天非常努力了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 工作狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 妈妈在等你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师 还有工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要整理一下 还要做明天的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏还要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天杏已经帮老师很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不用了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然和老师约定要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要帮忙到底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 告诉妈妈之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也说过一会再来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就恭敬不如从命了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杏 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做了好多工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师又漂亮又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿土要被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 小杏更可爱更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土田老师一定最喜欢小杏的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 杏还是小孩子 阿土他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师虽然是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过经常摔倒 老弄丢东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还总给土田老师和草野老师添麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 今天多亏杏帮忙了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么以后杏还要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么工作都告诉我哦 绝对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉钩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢 阿土老是在打游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 还很讨厌洋葱 总是不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以挑食呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本老师有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚园的大家老师都喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～ 不是指这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙昨天有没有好好听话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘可真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 我也会和山本老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏喜欢吃千层糕（mille-feuille）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千层糕很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕的话我喜欢法式栗子蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅呢前几天和哥哥去了新开的一家蛋糕店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个蛋糕自助店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哎呀 真是热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕自助店？是可以吃蛋糕吃到饱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子说话的时候 男孩子不要插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 我是山本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢小杏今天帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帮了老师大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就拜托小梅咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是少年侦探团与小梅的初恋情缘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}花丸侦探团
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}花丸初恋
